description: This highly desirable South Boston three-family property is now available for sale. This fully rented building, which features coin-operated laundry in the basement, generates $9,200 a month in rental income. Units 1 and 2 each offer four rooms, including two bedrooms and one bath, while Unit 3 boasts five rooms, with three bedrooms and one bath. Tenants cover all their own utilities, and the building is designed to operate as cost-effectively as possible to maximize an investor's annual return. Don't miss out on your chance to acquire this rarely available property type in one of Boston's largest real estate markets.
